{
  "texts": [
    "• Propose a new integration technique for detecting breast cancer that integrates multiple CNN models.",
    "When compared to other ways of learning, the suggested method was respectable for detecting BC-IDC tissues in breast cancer whole slide images (WSI).",
    "• Evaluation and comparison of the proposed model with other state-of-the-art deep learning models (MobileNet+DenseNet121, MobileNetV2+EfficientNetV2B0, etc.)",
    "to show its better or higher performance in regards to accuracy, precision, recall, F1-score, MCC, (ROC-AUC), and (AUPRC).",
    "• We are utilizing the knowledge transferred from multiple pre-trained models to enhance the accuracy and efficiency of detecting and classifying IDC tissues in the breast cancer histology images from Kaggle."
  ]
}